<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 12:20:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：俄罗斯诺瓦泰克公司在中国设立办事处，在制裁期间销售天然气--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russias-novatek-sets-up-china-office-market-gas-amid-sanctions-sources-2024-02-06/</link><description>据知情人士透露，俄罗斯天然气生产商诺瓦泰克正在组建一个新的中国团队，以探索该燃料的营销，因为美国的制裁阻碍了其价值数十亿美元的新北极项目的出口计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 11:23:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russias-novatek-sets-up-china-office-market-gas-amid-sanctions-sources-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>大众旗下奥迪削减布鲁塞尔工厂产量 - Automobilwoche</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-audi-reduces-output-brussels-plant-automobilwoche-2024-02-06/</link><description>据德国周刊《Automobilwoche》报道，大众汽车旗下豪华车部门奥迪已从 2 月 5 日起将其布鲁塞尔工厂的产量削减了两周，理由是零部件短缺。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 11:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-audi-reduces-output-brussels-plant-automobilwoche-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：利率反弹降温，中国指令反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-06/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 11:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国交易所限制部分对冲基金抛售股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exchanges-restrict-stock-selling-by-some-hedge-funds-2024-02-06/</link><description>四位基金经理和一位经纪人表示，中国证券交易所正在限制一些对冲基金的股票出售，这是稳定跌至五年低点的市场的最新尝试。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 10:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exchanges-restrict-stock-selling-by-some-hedge-funds-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>2024年巴基斯坦大选：新政府将面临哪些挑战？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/multiple-challenges-face-winner-pakistans-upcoming-general-election-2024-02-06/</link><description>巴基斯坦将于周四举行全国选举，选出新政府，多重危机困扰着这个拥有 2.41 亿人口的拥有核武器的南亚国家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 10:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/multiple-challenges-face-winner-pakistans-upcoming-general-election-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利 1 月外资基金净卖出 26 亿美元中国股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-funds-sold-net-us26-bln-china-equities-jan-morgan-stanley-2024-02-06/</link><description>摩根士丹利的数据显示，尽管估值低迷，但由于股市长期暴跌，全球投资者在一月份继续削减对中国股票的投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 10:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-funds-sold-net-us26-bln-china-equities-jan-morgan-stanley-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警船进入东海争议海域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-vessels-enter-disputed-waters-east-china-sea-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国海警表示，周二在钓鱼岛海域进行了巡逻。钓鱼岛是中国、日本和台湾都声称拥有主权的东海领土。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:49:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-vessels-enter-disputed-waters-east-china-sea-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>受英国石油公司和中国股票的支撑，富时 100 指数上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-set-snap-4-day-losing-streak-bp-shines-2024-02-06/</link><description>英国富时100指数周二走高，受益于行业重量级英国石油公司的乐观业绩，能源股上涨，而在世界第二大经济体承诺股市支持后，受中国影响的矿业和金融股上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-set-snap-4-day-losing-streak-bp-shines-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>英国石油公司和中国的刺激措施抵消了利率紧张情绪，欧洲股市小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/bp-earnings-china-stimulus-lift-european-stocks-open-2024-02-06/</link><description>欧洲股市周二小幅走高，英国石油公司的丰厚盈利帮助抵消了瑞银和北欧半导体的损失，而投资者则从中国遭受重创的金融市场的新刺激措施中得到了安慰。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/bp-earnings-china-stimulus-lift-european-stocks-open-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市因官方支持再度升温而大幅反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-rebound-sharply-renewed-talk-official-support-2024-02-06/</link><description>周二，遭受重创的中国股市创下两年来最大单日涨幅，一系列信号表明当局正在加强支持低迷市场的决心，人民币汇率也随之上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-rebound-sharply-renewed-talk-official-support-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国船只在马尔代夫用于科学研究-外交部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-vessel-maldives-being-used-scientific-research-foreign-ministry-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，一艘中国船只停靠马尔代夫港口进行的研究完全出于和平目的并增进科学认识，该船即将抵达这个岛国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 07:36:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-vessel-maldives-being-used-scientific-research-foreign-ministry-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>脱北者称口粮减少和市场依赖为由</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-defectors-cite-dwindling-food-rations-market-reliance-study-2024-02-06/</link><description>首尔统一部发布的一项研究显示，过去十年在韩国重新定居的大多数朝鲜人表示，他们从未在这个孤立的国家获得过政府口粮，不得不依靠非正式市场生存。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 07:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-defectors-cite-dwindling-food-rations-market-reliance-study-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国市场因政策提振前景而跃升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/view-china-markets-leap-prospect-policy-boost-2024-02-06/</link><description>周二，中国股市创下 14 个月以来的最大涨幅，人民币上涨，原因是国家支持市场的进一步迹象以及国家主席习近平将与金融监管机构讨论市场的新闻报道。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 06:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/view-china-markets-leap-prospect-policy-boost-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国限制，中国仍致力于提高芯片产量 - FT</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-aims-boost-chip-production-despite-us-restrictions-ft-2024-02-06/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周二报道，尽管美国努力遏制中国芯片制造商先进技术的发展，但中国芯片制造商预计最早将于今年生产下一代智能手机处理器。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-aims-boost-chip-production-despite-us-restrictions-ft-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国监管机构宣布加强卖空限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulator-unveils-more-curbs-short-selling-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周二表示，将暂停券商借入股票进行借贷，并限制所谓的证券转贷业务规模，作为进一步遏制卖空行为的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulator-unveils-more-curbs-short-selling-2024-02-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>